What you need to know:

Losing four points to minnows Comoros shows we are, not only not good enough to qualify, but also not good enough to be competitive in the finals, not withstanding it is a large 24-team affair.Our level is severely wanting despite the FKF, in the not so distant past, parroting, without any concrete plans whatsoever, about taking Kenya to the 2022 World Cup in Qatar. What a con!